summary: Blank Space parody Harry Potter style
title: Blank Space parody Harry Potter style
body:
Voldemort sings this for Harry Potter, obviously, featuring Lucius :)

(I wrote this in 2016 lmao I’m embarrassed )

Nice to meet you

Where you’ve been?

All these years I’ve been waiting.

Magic, madness and only sins

Saw you in Hogwarts and I thought,

Oh my god! Look at that face!
You look like your father James.

The games he played – do you wanna play?

I came hidden,

under a turban,

So that I could be by your side.

It was shocking, seeing you fly

And I knew you got your father’s genes

Coz every rule you’d bend

How come Fluffy became your friend

You were just a kid, undertrained

(And so easily you shot to fame!)

So are you gifted?

Or is it Dumbledore’s game?

I know ya’ scared of Dementors!

Their sight gives you a searing pain.

Got a long list of Death Eaters,

They’ll tell you I’m the lord.

They are all faithful servants,

And Bellatrix’s on the top!

Coz I’m strong and powerful

I’ve managed to come this far.

Left your parents breathless

And you with a nasty scar.

Got a long list of protestors!

(a side effect of fame.)

They call me You –know- who.

So scared- can’t even utter my name!

The boy who lived

The Chosen One

Because of me you’re having fun.

Read my mind

Anytime

You’re a speck Harry I am the sun.

Find out what you think

Can curse you before you blink

This is worse than what you think!

OH YES!

Screaming , crying, hurting scar

Harry you’ve come this far.

Wounded wizard, horrible pain

It’s all a part of this nasty game.

LUCIUS: 

Oh my god! Who is she?

The brightest witch I’ve ever seen

Red haired guy- sure a Weasley

I don’t wanna say but you make a great team.

So you’re in Gryffindor?

Slytherin’s not your piece of cake.

For that you’ve to be wicked

Creative smart and not fake.

Voldy: Got a long list of Death Eaters

They’ll tell you I am the king.

Belatrix, Narcissa, Lucius

My praise- they all sing!
Coz you’re a part of me,

I want you by my side.

Try Occlumency

Yet there’s no way to hide.

Got a long list of your soldiers

Who learn Dark Arts form you

To defend themselves

And Dumbledore too!

The thing you only deserve is Harry torture

Don’t say I didn’t say I didn’t warn ya’! (X2)

So is it gonna be forever

In Hogwarts you’ll hide?

Or shall I keep your place vacant, in case you change your side?

You all awfully good people,

Think that I am insane

My bloody souls is in pieces

This ain’t any Quidditch game!
Coz you’re young and stupid

I’ll help you from now on

It’ll make us stronger!

Anew benchmark will form

Even though I have no nose

(this is not what I chose)

I got my Nagini baby!

Life is a bed of rose!

summary: The  double album theory might be true . And also the speculation that this album was written before reputation might be true as...
body:
The double album theory might be true . And also the speculation that this album was written before reputation might be true as well.

What if half of the double album was written before reputation and the next half is the part that was written after reputation. Like the first part being about Taylor(me) and thus before reputation and the second about you .

I know it doesn’t make sense but…..*sighs*

summary: I cry and dance at the same time every time I think about it, because I'm so so happy but it will be almost impossible to tell...
body:
💗💗💗💗💗

Taylor come in Paris this week!! 🌈

I cry and dance at the same time every time I think about it, because I’m so so happy but it will be almost impossible to tell her how much I love her and how much she helped me with her music, and how wonderful she is, and even less to have a picture or an autograph. 🦋 I took my train tickets for Monday 27th, I would be in front of NRJ studio. I wouldn’t miss his return in France for anything in the world. It’s so surreal. 🌸💖

tags: i have so much love for this amazing girl
summary: I can’t believe it’s been a year since I was having the time of my life with my best friends singing at the top of my lungs &...
body:
I can’t believe it’s been a year since I was having the time of my life with my best friends singing at the top of my lungs & dancing in a stadium full of Swifties! How fitting is it that I got to see her perform the day before the one year anniversary of our night on the rep tour?! I’m dying over it! Listening to reputation will never not be an emotional experience for me after that night on the rep tour. This may have been Taylor’s biggest tour yet, but it felt like her most intimate. I was in the same stadium as her singing at the top of my lungs with her, dancing with her (I still have bruises on my knees from all the dancing & hitting the chair in front of me. I could not be contained! 😹) I was there with her & it was magical & emotional for me. This girl that has sang my heart & soul in so many songs & poured so much of herself out to share with us on this album & tour. This girl that saved me by giving me a release so many times when I felt like nobody understood me or what I was going through. She understood & she had been there & because of that I didn’t feel alone. For that I will always consider her a dear friend. Even though we’ve never met & she doesn’t know my name. She knows my heart & we are connected somehow & I am so thankful for that & for her. I can’t wait to see what she has for us next! I’m so ready for this journey with you all! ♥️ xoxo

@taylorswift @taylornation
